quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,70,"Sano ŵanganyao mu sajo syao akutugala (pakwakuya mwachitemachitema mwangali kusosa kaje umboni)."
  37,71,"Soni chisimu ŵapotele paujo pao ŵajinji (mu ŵandu) ŵandanda."
  37,72,"Soni chisimu twatumisye mwa ŵanganyao akutetela."
  38,49,"Achi ni chikumbusyo. Sano chisimu ŵawoga (wakun’jogopa Allah) akwete kupata malo gakuujila gambone nnope."
  38,50,"Matimbe Gandamo, gatigakaŵe geugulidwe milango kwaugulila ŵanganyao."
  38,51,"Takaŵe ali ajegeme (mwakwegama) kwalakweko, achiŵilasyaga kwalakweko isogosi yejinji ni yakumwa."
  39,34,"Akwete kupata ŵanganyao iliyose yatakaisacheje kwa M’mbuje gwao (Allah), gele ni malipilo ga ŵakolosya (masengo)."
  39,35,"Kuti Allah akaasiimaachisye ŵanganyao yakusakala yaŵapanganyisye, ni kwalipila malipilo gao pa yambone nnope yaŵaliji nkupanganya."
  39,36,"Ana Allah nganaŵa Jwakunkwanila kapolo Jwakwe? Ni akun’jogoyechesya ŵanganyao ayila (yaakuigalagatila) yangaŵaga Jwalakwe (Allah). Sano jwannechelele Allah kusokonechela, basi nganijukola nkun’jongola."
  40,13,"Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwaakunnosya ŵanganyammwe ilosyo Yakwe (yakulosya ukombosi Wakwe), ni akuntuluchisya lisiki (wula) kuumila kwinani, ni ngaakukumbuchila (kusyesyene) ikaŵeje ajula jwaakuwujila (kwa Allah pakutenda toba)."
  40,14,"Basi munnumbanjileje Allah mwakunswejechesya dini Jakwe, namuno achimakafili yachime."
  40,15,"(Jwalakwe Allah ni) Nsyene mauchimbichimbi gapenani kusyene, Nsyene Arishi (Chindanda Chaulungu), jukupelekaga maloŵe kwa lilamusi Lyakwe ku jwansachile mwa achikapolo Ŵakwe, kuti jutetele ya lisiku lyakusimangana (lisiku lya Kiyama)."